(110, 'photo/5302d5ab9a3c5.jpg', 'Kuching - Kayaking + City Tour', 0, '3D2N Kayaking + City Tour (Min 2 Person)', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"heading4\">3D2N Kayaking + City Tour</span><span class=\"contentArial-red\"><br /></span>Min 2pax<br /><br /><br /><span class=\"contentArial-red\">Description</span><br /></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>DAY 01</strong>&nbsp;<strong>ARRIVAL / CITY TOUR / CHECK IN (D)</strong><br />Upon arrival at the Kuching International Airport, meets and greets; and then proceed with Kuching City Tour.&nbsp; Experience the glorious heritage of people whose origins are shrouded in the mists of time.&nbsp; Tours include a visit to Sarawak museum, Kuching waterfront, the state parliament house, state mosque, main bazaar, civic centre and else.&nbsp; Dinner at local restaurant before check in</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>DAY 02</strong>&nbsp;<strong>BORNEO HIGHLAND ORANG UTAN KAYAKING ADVENTURE - 8 hrs (B/L/D)</strong><br />Breakfast at hotel, start the adventure with a visit to Semenggoh Wildlife centre to see the Orang Utan at feeding time.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Then proceed to paddle downstream from kampong Bengoh to kampong Semadang with breaks along the way for photo takes, fun swimming and lunch&nbsp;<strong>(picnic lunch).</strong>&nbsp; Behold the sights of massive limestone formation and picturesque mountains riddled with caves.&nbsp; Breathe in the fresh mountain air and soak in the serenity of the lush rainforest.&nbsp; Make a stop at kampong Danu, a friendly Bidayuh village and check out the carnivorous pitcher plant and some native plants and herbs.&nbsp; A truly not to be missed adventure for animal and nature lover!&nbsp; Dinner will be taken place at local restaurant before you back to hotel</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>DAY 03 DEPARTURE (B)</strong><br />Breakfast at hotel, free until time for airport transfers</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><table style=\"width: 450px; height: 124px;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" background=\"http://pinsingtravel.com/images/frame_a.jpg\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><br /></span></span></td></tr><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" background=\"http://pinsingtravel.com/images/frame_b.jpg\"><table style=\"width: 96%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"contentArial-red\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></span><span class=\"contentArial-black\"><p>- Confirmation subject to room&nbsp; &amp; transport availability<br />- Surcharge during weekend &amp; public holidays (for hotel room)</p></span></span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>');
